Installation.

Dialplan XML.

<extension name="outbound">
  <condition field="destination_number" expression="^(8084)$">
    <action application="socket" data="127.0.0.1:8084 sync full"/>
  </condition>
</extension>

<extension name="hangup">
  <condition field="destination_number" expression="^(hangup)$">
    <action application="playback" data="prepaid-no-enough-credit-stop.gsm"/>
    <action application="hangup"/>
  </condition>
</extension>

Requirements.

* ruby (>= 1.8 - 1.9+ is preferred)
* activerecord
* rake
* freeswitcher
* freeswitch with mod_nibblebill

